  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><strong><strong>Two great opportunities to meet Santa </strong></strong></p>
<p>For all Ingham's guests on a Santa Short Break arriving in <a href="/{localLink:umb://document/9dee14339770490983c23ccc11530d35}" title="Santa Breaks in Levi">Levi</a> or <a href="/{localLink:umb://document/8d7194d440db47e2b48d371f537fb9db}" title="Santa Breaks in Yllas">Yllas</a>, we have included two exciting opportunities.</p>
<p><strong><strong>Meet Santa in his magical workshop, elves and all!</strong></strong></p>
<p>On day 2 there's a magical jaunt in store - a visit to one of Santa's enchanting workshops where you will enjoy an exclusive private family meeting with Santa himself! You can also take part in supervised festive games and help the elves bake gingerbread biscuits and make decorations. Outdoors you can meet Comet the Reindeer, catch the snowmobile train or have great fun tobogganing or playing football in the snow. </p>
<p><strong><strong>Festive Dinner with Santa </strong></strong></p>
<p>On the last evening of Santa Short Breaks, we have included a special festive gala dinner with Santa (even for guests who are booked on a self-catering basis), where you will enjoy a traditional British Christmas food and Lappish specialities. There will be party games and a disco but the highlight of the evening will be a visit from Santa and his reindeer and all children will have the opportunity to meet him individually and receive a small memento gift and certificate. We hope this will be fun and memorable way to end your Santa Break.</p>
<p>In addition, our 7 night holidays also offer dinner with Santa and his reindeer for all guests arriving 7, 14, 21, 25 December 2019 in <a href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi">Levi</a>, <a href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka">Saariselka</a> and <a href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas">Yllas</a>.</p>]]></bodyText>
